		<RichText x="66" y="1008" fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="16" fontStyle="normal" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff" width="312" height="20" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.7490196078431373">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="16" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">枯风之佑：生命盾，继承25%特瓦林生命值。</p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/深渊魔龙%B7特瓦林.assets/Image_15.png')" x="64" y="64" blendMode="normal">
		</BitmapImage>
		<RichText x="738" y="223" width="424" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">特瓦林从远处猛地冲来，用爪子划过平台，造成<span color="#b9b9b9">100%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="447" width="422" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">特瓦林将头甩上平台，造成<span color="#b9b9b9">100%</span><span>伤害，停留数秒后离去。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="671" width="424" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">特瓦林下潜，并从对面超远处平台冒出，蓄力施放巨大的黯渊球，对整个平台造成<span color="#b8b8b8">100%</span><span>伤害</span><span color="#ffbfbf">(闪避帧无效)</span><span>。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/深渊魔龙%B7特瓦林.assets/Image_16.png')" x="719" y="137">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/深渊魔龙%B7特瓦林.assets/Image_17.png')" x="1391" y="361">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/深渊魔龙%B7特瓦林.assets/Image_18.png')" x="1393" y="138">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/深渊魔龙%B7特瓦林.assets/Image_19.png')" x="1391" y="585">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/深渊魔龙%B7特瓦林.assets/Image_20.png')" x="721" y="586">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/深渊魔龙%B7特瓦林.assets/Image_21.png')" x="719" y="361">
		</BitmapImage>
		<RichText x="1410" y="223" width="424" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">特瓦林趴在平台上，吐出漆黑龙息，持续造成<span color="#b8b8b8">50%</span><span>伤害，从一侧开始扫过平台大部分区域。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="447" width="422" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">特瓦林离开平台，一左一右地发射黑渊弹，每次2个，每个造成<span color="#b8b8b8">50%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="671" width="439" height="143" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">特瓦林怒吼，在所有平台周期性产生6道星门阵，每个星门阵于玩家所在平台降下蚀星，造成<span color="#b8b8b8">30%</span><span>伤害；特瓦林倒地则暂停施放，恢复后继续；破坏2次护盾后施放。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/深渊魔龙%B7特瓦林.assets/Image_22.png')" x="1268" y="395" blendMode="normal">
		</BitmapImage>
