		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/深渊魔龙%B7特瓦林.assets/Image_27.png')" x="596" y="395" blendMode="normal">
		</BitmapImage>
		<RichText x="738" y="895" width="431" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">特瓦林倒地时会展开「深黯护盾」，该护罩继承<span color="#ffdfbf">15%生命值</span><span>，后续出现则为</span><span color="#ffdfbf">7.5%生命值</span><span>，只接受元素伤害；破坏后</span><span color="#ffdfbf">失去15%</span><span>生命值。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
