		</BitmapImage>
		<RichText x="1410" y="896" width="431" height="39" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="16" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">减伤：在特瓦林从地下升起、「深邃的悲楚」吼叫时、「夜穹的谵呓」施放时、「昏黑的号恸」蓄力时均具有<span color="#ffdfbf">95%减伤</span><span>。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
